# Distribution / packaging
src/include/
# Sphinx auto-populates src/docs/ (run make_docs after the first build).
# Track the directory itself — the bundle builder SystemExits silently at
# packaging time if it's missing — but ignore its generated contents.
src/docs/*
!src/docs/.gitignore
